        <abstract> 
<p>Convinced <hi rend="italic">Cross and self fertilisation</hi> is of permanent value, though an extremely dry, special subject. Thinks it will sell for many years and suggests a printing of 1500 copies. Asks that a good indexer be found and put to work. Appleton has agreed to publish it</p>  
<p>and <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>, [2d ed.], if Murray’s will supply stereotype plates.</p> 
        </abstract>
